CHRONOLOGICAL TABLE. xxxiii

AGE OF Rc. HORACE. 1 1 54 Tiberius marries Julia, and carries on war with the

Dalmatians and Pannonians. Drusus erects forts in Germany, and returns to Rome to take the praetorship.

10 55 Augustus visits Lugdunum (Lyons). An altar erected to him there on July 1. Tiberius and Drusus carry on war.

9 56 Augustus returns to Rome on Jan. 30. Tiberius has an ovatio sor his successes. Drusus dies from an accident.

8 57 Tiberius governor of Gaul. Death of Maecenas, and of Horace on Nov. 27, a sew days before he had completed his 57th year.
